  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Spatially Localized Spectral Conv: ",
    "text_level": 1,
    "bbox": [
      432,
      433,
      561,
      454
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "list",
    "sub_type": "text",
    "list_items": [
      "· $\\checkmark$ Spectral convolution is scale equivariant ",
      "·X Global in nature-ill fit for vision tasks ",
      "·We propose Localized Spectral Convolution $\\checkmark$ Maintains equivariance $\\checkmark$ Captures local features "
    ],
    "bbox": [
      446,
      456,
      607,
      563
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Non-Linearity and Pooling: ",
    "text_level": 1,
    "bbox": [
      434,
      586,
      565,
      606
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "·For any function $\\sigma$ , its scale equivariant version, $\\sigma _ { e q } ( { \\bf x } ) = { \\bf y }$ ,can be defined as ",
    "bbox": [
      450,
      607,
      616,
      650
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "equation",
    "text": "$$\n\\mathbf {Y} [ k ] = \\mathcal {F} \\left(\\sigma \\circ \\mathcal {F} ^ {- 1} \\left(\\mathbf {X} \\left[ - | k |: | k | \\right]\\right)\\right) [ k ]\n$$",
    "text_format": "latex",
    "bbox": [
      463,
      654,
      609,
      690
    ],
    "page_idx": 0,
    "img_path": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "where $\\mathbf { X } = { \\mathcal { F } } ( \\mathbf { x } )$ and $\\mathbf { Y } = { \\mathcal { F } } ( \\mathbf { y } )$ ",
    "bbox": [
      457,
      705,
      575,
      729
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Classification and Scaling: ",
    "text_level": 1,
    "bbox": [
      432,
      756,
      531,
      776
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "list",
    "sub_type": "text",
    "list_items": [
      "· Invariance is not desirable for scaling ",
      "·Classification loss should not increase at a higher scale ",
      "·We propose scale consistency loss "
    ],
    "bbox": [
      446,
      778,
      613,
      864
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "equation",
    "text": "$$\n\\mathcal {L} _ {c o n} = \\max  \\left(\\mathcal {L} (\\hat {\\boldsymbol {y}} [ k ], y) - \\mathcal {L} (\\hat {\\boldsymbol {y}} [ k - 1 ], y), 0\\right).\n$$",
    "text_format": "latex",
    "bbox": [
      452,
      881,
      612,
      906
    ],
    "page_idx": 0,
    "img_path": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "Here, $\\hat { y } [ k ]$ is the prediction of classifier $\\mathcal { M }$ at $k ^ { \\mathrm { t h } }$ scale. ",
    "bbox": [
      452,
      921,
      613,
      961
    ],
    "page_idx": 0
  },
  {
    "type": "text",
    "text": "RESULTS ",
    "text_level": 1,
    "bbox": [
